# Codebase Context

## Architecture
- This is a monorepo with three main packages: api, web, and shared
- The API uses Express with TypeORM
- The web client is Next.js

## Common patterns
- To add a new API endpoint, see src/api/routes/users.ts as an example
- Database migrations are in src/api/migrations
- Services handle business logic, repositories handle data access
